WEBVTT

1
01:40:21.790 --> 01:40:23.450 
要学会跳舞吗
Want to learn how to dance ?

2
01:40:23.530 --> 01:40:25.620 
你得在跳舞时触碰到那个人
You gotta touch someone when you dance.

3
01:40:25.700 --> 01:40:28.390 
我不会伤害你 好吗
I'm not going to hurt you, all right?

4
01:40:28.470 --> 01:40:30.060 
就放在那里
Just put it right there.

5
01:40:30.140 --> 01:40:32.130 
我把我的手放在那里
I take my hand and put it up here.

6
01:40:33.040 --> 01:40:35.200 
看着我的脚 雷 看着我的脚
Watch my feet, Ray. Watch my feet.

7
01:40:35.310 --> 01:40:36.640 
韵律 韵律
The rhythm, the rhythm.

8
01:40:37.580 --> 01:40:39.040 
可以吗
All right?

9
01:40:39.110 --> 01:40:41.440 
你跳舞时 不能一直看着我的脚
You can't watch my feet the whole time,

10
01:40:41.510 --> 01:40:43.410 
所以你得往上看
so you're gonna have to look up.

11
01:40:43.480 --> 01:40:47.980 
当我叫你看时 你就往上看 慢慢的
When I tell you to, just look up, real slow.

12
01:40:48.050 --> 01:40:49.320 
继续移动
Just keep moving.

13
01:40:50.060 --> 01:40:51.220 
好 准备好了
Okay, you ready?

